# Use Fallowing link to install npm and Node.js
	https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-install-node-js-on-ubuntu-18.04/

Run this command on the directry that you wish to create Node project and Answer the quactions
	npm init

Express
	npm install --save express

# You have to create the your own server for nodejs.
# So create a new file named server.js

Add this library to prevent restsrting the server in each and every change. # -dev beacuse this library is use only for the development
	npm --save-dev nodemon


